'''T細胞淋巴瘤'''({{lang|en|T-cell lymphoma}})包括四種影響[[T细胞|T细胞]]的[[淋巴瘤|淋巴瘤]]類型。這些解釋或許能說明十分之一的[[非霍奇金氏淋巴瘤|非霍奇金氏淋巴瘤]]之情況。 <ref name="The Lymphomas">{{cite web |url=http://www.leukemia-lymphoma.org/attachments/National/br_1161891669.pdf |title=The Lymphomas |accessdate=2008-04-07 |author= |authorlink= |coauthors= |date=May 2006 |format=PDF |publisher=The Leukemia & Lymphoma Society |page=2 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080706143003/http://www.leukemia-lymphoma.org/attachments/National/br_1161891669.pdf |archivedate=2008-07-06 }}</ref>

T細胞淋巴瘤伴隨著[[人類疱疹病毒第四型|人類疱疹病毒第四型]]及[[人類T淋巴細胞白血病病毒1|人類T淋巴細胞白血病病毒1]](Human T-cell leukemia virus-1)之病症而來。<ref name="pmid18954748">{{cite journal |author=Vose JM |title=Peripheral T-cell non-Hodgkin's lymphoma |journal=Hematol. Oncol. Clin. North Am. |volume=22 |issue=5 |pages=997–1005, x |date=October 2008 |pmid=18954748 |doi=10.1016/j.hoc.2008.07.010 |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0889-8588(08)00106-8 |access-date=2014-04-10 |archive-date=2019-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190218055159/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0889-8588(08)00106-8 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==類型==
四種T细胞淋巴瘤類型為：

* [[血管中心性淋巴瘤|血管中心性淋巴瘤]](Angiocentric lymphoma)
* [[皮膚T細胞淋巴瘤|皮膚T細胞淋巴瘤]](Cutaneous T cell lymphoma)：[[塞扎病|塞扎病]](Sézary's disease)及[[蕈樣肉芽腫|蕈樣肉芽腫]](Mycosis fungoides)
* [[間變性大細胞淋巴瘤|間變性大細胞淋巴瘤]](Anaplastic large-cell lymphoma)
* [[血管免疫母細胞性T細胞淋巴瘤|血管免疫母細胞性T細胞淋巴瘤]](Angioimmunoblastic T-cell lymphoma)

更多"T细胞淋巴瘤"的各種分類方案之信息可以參見主條目[[淋巴瘤|淋巴瘤]]。

==流行病學==
在[[流行病学|流行病学]]上，涉及[[淋巴增殖性疾病|同一類血細胞的癌症]](Lymphoproliferative disorders)，8％的病例是屬於"成熟性T細胞淋巴瘤"({{lang|en|mature T cell lymphomas}})。<ref name="isbn0-7817-5007-5">{{cite book|author=Turgeon, Mary Louise|title=Clinical hematology: theory and procedures|url=https://archive.org/details/clinicalhematolo0004turg|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|location=Hagerstown, MD
|year=2005|isbn=0-7817-5007-5|quote=Frequency of lymphoid neoplasms.  (Source:  Modified from WHO Blue Book on Tumour of Hematopoietic and Lymphoid Tissues. 2001, p. 2001.)|page=[https://archive.org/details/clinicalhematolo0004turg/page/283 283]}}</ref> 而從這些病例中、有2％是屬於"前體T淋巴細胞瘤"(precursor T lymphoblastic)，另2％是屬於"皮膚T細胞淋巴瘤"(cutaneous T cell lymphoma)。<ref name="isbn0-7817-5007-5"/>

